tom: 0; padding-left: 4px;"><strong>Intelligence API. </strong><span>A numb=
er of new products are being built around OpenAI&#8217;s API and a bunch of=
 incumbent products are re-architecting themselves around OpenAI&#8217;s AP=
I. Unlike most APIs, which serve non-core functions, the OpenAI Intelligenc=
e API is core to many of these product experiences.&#160;</span></p></li><l=
