0; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0; margin-left: 20p=
x;"><em><strong>Here&#8217;s the hard thing about easy things:</strong><spa=
n> if everyone can do something, there&#8217;s no advantage to doing it, bu=
t you still have to do it anyway just to keep up.</span></em></p></blockquo=
te><p style=3D"color: #404040; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: =
0 0 20px 0;"><span>In just a couple of months, we&#8217;re already at a poi=
